# dwm installation

pacman -S xorg-server xorg-int xorg-randr xorg-xsetroot nitrogen picom 
clone, make clean install from official git repos of dwm, dmenu, st
cp /etc/X11/xinitrc ~/.xinitrc
remove last 4-5 lines from .xinitrc and replace with 'exec dwm' (refer xinitrc in repository)
append 'startx' in ./bash_profile (refer bash_profile in repository)
